{"tid":380113,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"西銅（358）中期純利增51.4%至9.7億人幣","createTime":"2017-08-30T00:47:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T17:13:25.000Z","uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"09d6f152d91c018341a9938f603463c8ba4968a7","tid":380113,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T00:47:59.000Z","msg":"《國企紅籌》江西銅中期純利增５１﹒４％至９﹒７億人幣，不派息 　　《經濟通通訊社３０日專訊》江西銅業（００３５８）公布截至６月底止中期業績，純利９﹒７４億元（人民幣．下同），比去年同期增５１﹒４１％。每股基本盈利０﹒２８元，不派發中期股息。　　期內，營業收入按年增８﹒９６％至９７７﹒６０億元。毛利按年增３１％至３１﹒８億元。（ａｌ）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN270830251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.etnet.com.hk%2Fwww%2Ftc%2Fnews%2Fcategorized_news_detail.php%3Fcategory%3Dlatest%26newsid%3DETN270830251&d=6ZuNabq%2BDfy2A1ObZL4X3Z4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=140c34c4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.etnet.com.hk/www/tc/news/categorized_news_detail.php?category=latest&amp;newsid=ETN270830251</a>"},{"pid":"500382f793dc2e66270718e9c16d313aca6f2b5d","tid":380113,"uid":57076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T00:51:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e013c76c499a14f04a3592ae25f9ff2c1159bf9c","tid":380113,"uid":44808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:21:58.000Z","msg":"勁假時段都係開紅燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03af12aca3745488e8ba6963cf6696eb63cbcc8a","tid":380113,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T01:56:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>勁假時段都係開紅燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開市都跌埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f16e8fe24b79dfbcc511